text: Shosse Entuziastov may refer to: * Shosse Entuziastov (Kalininsko- Solntsevskaya Line), a Moscow Metro station, Russia * Shosse Entuziastov (Moscow Central Circle), a Moscow Metro station, Russia * Entuziastov Highway, after which Shosse Entuziastov (Kalininsko-Solntsevskaya Line) is named.
title: Shosse Entuziastov
